{
 "file": "_STG02.bin",
 "source_size": 39476,
 "built_size": 42255,
 "edits": [
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1245",
   "jp_len": 58,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "あいうえおかダチッツテ{01}デ、·{00}！ゃ{01}Mくみな、{00}{01}！レ{00}M動ほな、{00}{01}ぁ可恶……！还打不倒吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15161718191a1b6566676869016a020400064201131e3e3302000106830013c63c3302000115e7c4e7de0909ef97e7f7e7f5e7b5e848e802ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x129a",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那个、敌方的机动装甲{00}比预想中要难缠……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e82802e7e3d0e7b4e7e4ef30e98febdb00e825ea5ae7e6c0ef2ae866ec3409090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12b3",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "恐怕是那种、{00}为新人类专门开发的新型机吧",
   "zh_hex": "15eb33e958e7b6e7b7e7d10200e7c1ef8ab4e841eb4be90ce7fae870e7b4ef8ae977e7e4e7d0000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12ea",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "蠢货！敌人不过区区2架而已！",
   "zh_hex": "15e94beaf5ef97e7e3efb2e7b5ef36ef35ef35ef5fe99de89cef3aef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12fe",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "无论如何、{00}都要把那架机动装甲完好无损地捕获！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dce8dce7f08a0200e840ef2ae81be7b7e99de7e4ef30e98febdbe87ee7c7e7dcea28bfcfe9d806000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x133d",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "牙买加那混蛋、净说得轻巧……！",
   "zh_hex": "15ebd7efa3e854e7b7ea41ea6d02ecb0e7ede80ae990ec130909ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1373",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "队长、我们该怎么办？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c9ef3402efcce7bbe898e7f2e7bde8ea0500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x139a",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "既然是命令、那就只能干了、不过……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8c4e7efe7b6e853e94e02e7b7e7c5ef32e7c6e8d3e7ba02e7b5ef36090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13b1",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不过想毫发无伤地拿下、{00}那可就难说了！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b5ef36e7e6ea0ae870e7dce8f9bfe9a7890200e7b7e7c4e7c5e866e7ede7ba0600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13f1",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "又来新的敌人了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8f1efcfef8ae7b4e7e3efb2e7baef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1416",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不妙",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b5ecc70000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x141f",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "要应付这么多敌人、能量余量实在堪忧",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ae873e97ee7b9e7bde7e9e7e3b402e7c6e851eb27e851e87fef29ed46ee1d00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x143e",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你那边怎么样、西格？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b7e899e7f2e7bde7da02e7f8e824050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x148a",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……原来如此。你那边也一样吗",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8e4efcfe7f0e7ca03e7b8e7b7e899e7c0efb6e7dae8020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x149f",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……西格",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7f8e8240000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14a6",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看来敌人、是冲着这架艾尔美斯来的",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6efcfe7e3efb202e7b6e95ee86de7b9e99de8d6e7e1e9f4e7c8efcfe7b4000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14bf",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我上前去当诱饵、{00}西格你就趁那个空当……",
   "zh_hex": "158bb2bae7ebc4eb44ed190200e7f8e824e7b8e7c5e9eae7b7e828e93fc4090900000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14f5",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不行",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b5efd60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1519",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为什么？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1e7dde7bd050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1520",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "都被逼到这种地步了、{00}还能有别的办法吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e840e7f1ebf6e7d7e7b9e7d1bfea93e7ba0200e7f7e7c6e7cbe7e5e7b4e8eae84ee80205000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1556",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "办法……是没有、{00}可即便如此、我也会想办法",
   "zh_hex": "15e8eae84e0909e7b6e7d8e7cb0200e7c4e855e8fae7f0e7ca028be7c0e7e2e7e6e8eae84e0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1585",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "西格？你在说什么……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f8e82405e7b8ef29e7ede7dde7bd09090500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15b0",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "两个人一起活着撑过这场战争、我们可是{00}这么约好的",
   "zh_hex": "15e97de828efb2efb6e847e8d4e86dea29ef36e7b9e876ef28e85202efcce7bbe7c4e7b600e7b9e7bde9ace7c7e7b40000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15ce",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "再乱来、再勉强、也要两人一起找出活路",
   "zh_hex": "15e80be976efcf02e80beb2ae8ad02e7c0ef2ae97defb2efb6e847e9d2efbee8d4e8d20000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15ed",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……明白了吗、瑟拉？",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef39e809e7bae80202e8aae7c2050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x161f",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵呵……真坚强啊……西格你",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3def3d0909e820eb80e8ade7c30909e7f8e824e7b800000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x164a",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "坚强？要论实战的本事、你可在我之上",
   "zh_hex": "15eb80e8ad05ef2ae8dce87fef28e7b4efa6efb802e7b8e7c4ef29efcce7cdef4c0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x165f",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我只是不肯认输",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef32e7b6e7b5e93de8a0e8b9000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x168c",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不肯认输吗……不过、那样也不坏",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e93de8a0e8b9e8020909e7b5ef3602e7b7e7dae7c0e7b5e9ed000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16a5",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……嗯、岂止不坏、简直好得很",
   "zh_hex": "150909e86502eac3e869e7b5e9ed02e9abe875e7c7e80ae9810000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16bd",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "给那边那帮得意忘形的家伙{00}狠狠来上一击、也挺有意思！",
   "zh_hex": "15e839e7b7e899e7b7e910e80aef3cea4dec67e7b4e7dfe7fd00ec7aec7ad9b287e7cc02e7c0eb5ce7cbef3ca60600000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16e1",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……上吧、西格！",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef4ce7d002e7f8e824ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1708",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……嗯！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e865060000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1735",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不好……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e7c70909ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x176f",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……西格！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7f8e824ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17a7",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "抱歉、西格……我们的约定……",
   "zh_hex": "15e922e92702e7f8e8240909efcce7bbe7b4e9ace8670909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17e8",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "瑟拉……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8aae7c20909ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1820",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎、怎会如此……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f202e7f2e7e2e7f0e7ca0909ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x185b",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我、我的阿普萨拉斯……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcc02efcce7b4e7d2e838e83be7c2e7c8090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1897",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……嗯？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e86505000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18bb",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "确认阿普萨拉斯航路上发生交战！{00}友军正遭敌包围！",
   "zh_hex": "15e88ce8a0e7d2e838e83be7c2e7c8e9c1e8d2b2e870b6e861ef280600e960e7e0ef3beb1ee7e3eabbe9de0600000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18f6",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哼、是弗拉纳冈的新人类机吗{00}……别去管它",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b302e7b6e9b5e7c2e882eb7ee7b4ef8ab4e841e7e4e802000909e7e5e7ebe93be97800000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1929",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哥哥！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e9bce9bcef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x194c",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "没有什么比完成阿普萨拉斯更要紧的事、{00}回所罗门、爱娜",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d8e7cbe7dde7bde825e87ee837e7d2e838e83be7c2e7c8e952ef2aeaede7b4a902008ce7fbe7ece90c02e8d5e7ea00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19ad",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎么了、爱娜！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f2e7bde7ba02e8d5e7eaef970500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19d3",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不、那道命令、恕我无法服从",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b502e7b7e82ae853e94e02eb048be7dce84ee9f1e88a00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a02",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "爱娜！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d5e7eaef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a24",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我不能对友军见死不救！{00}我这就前去救援！",
   "zh_hex": "158be7b5e7c6e7bee960e7e0e85ca7e7b5e8ca06008be7b9e7c5bae7ebe8cae8630600000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a79",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阿普萨拉斯、出击！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d2e838e83be7c2e7c802efbee7ccef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a9d",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "爱娜这孩子……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d5e7eae7b9e956e88609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ac0",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "基尼亚斯少将、我们该如何是好？",
   "zh_hex": "15e829e896e7d6e7c8eface84a02efcce7bbe898e7f0efbce7b6e7c7050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1aec",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……事到如今也没办法、{00}继续监视阿普萨拉斯",
   "zh_hex": "150909a9e7d7e7f0a2e7c0e7d8e8eae84e0200e9d6e9aded8de9d9e7d2e838e83be7c2e7c80000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b06",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "至少也得把实战数据拿到手、{00}不然就太亏了",
   "zh_hex": "15e897b1e7c0e80ae81be87fef28e914e8cce9a7e7d7ae0200e7b5e7efe7c5e86aeab7e7ba00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b39",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b5a",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……哼",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8b30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b61",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "罢了、卖基西莉亚少将一个人情、{00}也不算坏",
   "zh_hex": "15eaefe7ba02ec4ce829e7f8e81ee7d6b1e84a87e828b4e88b0200e7c0e7b5e889e9ed00000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ba0",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是……机动装甲？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b60909e7e4ef30e98febdb05000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1bda",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是爱娜·萨哈林、特来救援二位！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6e8d5e7eaef4be83be7e8e9b702e7cfefcfe8cae863ea13e834ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1bf2",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我用阿普萨拉斯杀出一条血路！{00}请趁机后退！",
   "zh_hex": "158bd8e7d2e838e83be7c2e7c8e89baf87e9d4e9f6e8d20600e83ae9eae7e4e7fee8800600000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c27",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "太好了！这份救援、我感激不尽！",
   "zh_hex": "15e86ae7c7e7baef97e7b9ea22e8cae86302efcce87de9b9e7b5e8f2ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c5e",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不好！退路被封死了！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e7c7ef97e880e8d2e7f1eb83ef6ae7baef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c92",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "万事休矣……",
   "zh_hex": "15e9f8efb8e90eed9209090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cc7",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什、什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dd02e7dde7bdef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cf6",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好、停火！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c702e934e8daef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d1d",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "布拉德队长！",
   "zh_hex": "15e831e7c2e82ce7c9ef34ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d57",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你平安无事啊！瑟拉！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e887e7fce7dcefb8e7c3ef97e8aae7c2ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d7c",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "艾因、还有队长也来了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d6ef3302e7f7e7cbe7c9ef34e7c0efcfe7ba0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1dac",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "西格中尉和瑟蕾因少尉、{00}看来都平安无事啊",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f8e824c086e7d3e8aae84cef33b1860200e7f6d9e840e887e7fce7dca9e7c30000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1dc6",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嗯？好像还有另一架机动装甲……",
   "zh_hex": "15e86505e7c7e8e9e7f7e7cbe99befb6e99de7e4ef30e98febdb090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1df9",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是爱娜·萨哈林",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6e8d5e7eaef4be83be7e8e9b70000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e03",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "试飞途中得知二位被包围、便赶来救援",
   "zh_hex": "15e91dea45ebf5ef4ee80ae85aea13e834e7f1eabbe9de02e8faea04efcfe8cae863000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e40",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "原来如此",
   "zh_hex": "15e8e4efcfe7f0e7ca0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e4b",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、爱娜·萨哈林小姐、{00}还请再陪我们一程",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e8d5e7ea04e83be7e8e9b7e83ee9210200e7f7e83ae80bef428be7bb87ea7d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e83",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看来该开始反击了吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6efcfe898e7fae908e87ce7cce7bae7d0000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1eae",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "布拉德中佐、本舰的指挥就交给贵官了",
   "zh_hex": "15e831e7c2e82cef4eefba02efa6e7d4e7b4e8c0e949e7c5e861e839e930ef92e7ba000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ec2",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "MS队、准备出击！就此击退敌部队！",
   "zh_hex": "15efa7ef9ee7c902e87ae877efbee7ccef97e7c5e7cae7cce880e7e3ef70e7c9ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1eff",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好、就趁现在！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c702e7c5e9eae82fef29ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f2f",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶！我才不会就这样乖乖挨打！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7deef97efcce836e7b5e7e2e7c5e7b9e7dae9a3e9a3eb8ae7f5ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f74",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呜哦哦——！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d9e919e919ebafebafef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fd4",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "快、快离开！你是想送命吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e85f02e85fe901e7faef97e7b8e7b6e7e6e9bae853e802ef9705000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2021",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我不能再这样看着伙伴一个个被击倒了！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b5e7c6e80be7b9e7dae7f6e86de7fdea72efb6e828e828e7f1e7cce848e7baef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2094",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你是！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b6ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20cd",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "爱娜·萨哈林！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d5e7eaef4be83be7e8e9b7ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20f2",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……竟会这样！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909ef2ce7e2e7b9e7daef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x211e",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎么办、大佐？就算想回收爱娜小姐……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f2e7bde8ea02efa5efba05e7c5e889e7e6ef52e926e8d5e7eae83ee9210909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2155",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是啊、要是后方被突袭、{00}就顾不上去搜寻她了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e7c302ef2ae7b6e7fed0e7f1e8b6e9ae0200e7c5ea1fe7b5b2e7ebed6defe2e88ee7ba000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2174",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "眼下、也只能专心击破敌部队了",
   "zh_hex": "15e90bef4d02e7c0ef32e7c6eb4be82de7ccef6de7e3ef70e7c9e7ba00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x218b",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "MS队、加紧击破敌人！",
   "zh_hex": "15efa7ef9ee7c902e854eaede7ccef6de7e3efb2ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21c2",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "敌人是机动装甲？可是、我也只能拼了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e3efb2e7b6e7e4ef30e98febdb05e7c4e7b602efcce7c0ef32e7c6ea66e7baef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21f4",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "冲过来了……？{00}想要打倒这架阿普萨拉斯……",
   "zh_hex": "15e95eef36d9e7ba09090500e7e6ef2ae7f5e848e7b9e99de7d2e838e83be7c2e7c8090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x220e",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可这是哥哥的梦想！绝不能让它被毁掉！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b9e7b6e9bce9bce7b4ea40e7e6ef97e91ce7b5e7c6e7f9e978e7f1e97ce9d3ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x224a",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这声音……是女人！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9ea8aea710909e7b6efadefb2ef97050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x227b",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "凭你这种为了女人就拿命去拼的软蛋、{00}也想打倒我！？",
   "zh_hex": "15ea49e7b8e7b9e7d1e7c1e7bab0b4e7c5e9a7e853e7ebea66e7b4eb47ea6d0200e7c0e7e6e7f5e8488b06050000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22bc",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "随你怎么说！结果、我会用实力来证明！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9a1e7b8e7f2e7bde7edef97e868e87102efcce7e2efb3e87fefb0efcfeba3ef39ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22f3",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嚯……好胆量！我看上你了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9dd0909e7c7edaee851068be7f6b2e7b8e7ba060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2306",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "照这样、看来能让我玩个痛快！{00}哈哈哈哈！",
   "zh_hex": "15ea1ae7b9e7da02e7f6d9e7c6e7f98be970e828ea0be85f0600e7e8e7e8e7e8e7e80600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2345",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "老子最看不惯女人出现在战场上了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9cae886e8c5e7f6e7b5ecd6efadefb2efbee82fef29ef28e876ef4ce7baef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x235e",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……把你碾碎！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e81be7b8ed95ebe0ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2389",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这话、该由我来说才对",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e81f02e898e8a6efccefcfe7ede836e7be000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2396",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对只凭外表来判断对手的蠢货、{00}我可没必要手下留情",
   "zh_hex": "15e7beef32ea49e8f7e9e7d9eb29e982e7beaee7b4e94beaf502008be7c4e7d8e860ef2aae89e98ce88b000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23ba",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "要后悔、就到阴间去慢慢后悔吧！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ae7feeb8602e7c5e7d7eb22e8fce7ebe979e979e7feeb86e7d0ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23e8",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "切！口气倒不小！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3fef97eabde8ede848e7b5e83eef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x241e",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只能眼睁睁看着伙伴一个个倒下……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32e7c6e90bed90ed90e7f6e86de7fdea72efb6e828e828e848ef4d09090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x243b",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我绝不想让SIDE2的惨剧再次重演！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce91ce7b5e7e6e7f9ef9eef62ef96ef9fef5fe7b4ed5decb5e80be864e8a1ea2fef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x246b",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "SIDE、SIDE2……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef9eef62ef96ef9f02ef9eef62ef96ef9fef5f09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2490",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7beef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2497",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那样的屠杀、绝不能再让它重演！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7dae7b4ed4fe89b02e91ce7b5e7c6e80be7f9e978e8a1ea2fef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24b3",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为此、我一定要打倒你们这些吉翁！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1e7ca028b87e867ef2ae7f5e848e7b8e7bbe7b9e8a4e7d9ee880600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2542",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎么了？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f2e7bde7ba050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2567",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "名字……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8ace98009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25ab",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "刚才是头一回吧、你叫我『瑟拉』",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bce836e7b6e92eefb6ef52e7d002e7b8e8c1efcc0ce8aae7c20d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25e4",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊、啊啊……是这样吗……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c302e7c3e7c30909e7b6e7b9e7dae8020909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2611",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "西格头一回认真地面对我……我很高兴",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f8e824e92eefb6ef52e8a0e820ef63e862e7beefcc0909efcce981e812eaba0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x262e",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我好像、要重新爱上你了",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7c7e8e902ef2ae8a1ef8ae8d5ef4ce7b8e7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x265a",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！这种时候、你在说什么呢……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def97e7b9e7d1ef2dea3902e7b8ef29e7ede7dde7bde9070909ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2688",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我之所以自称『瑟拉』、并不是因为{00}喜欢这名字",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcce7cde7fbe7f3efb5ea010ce8aae7c20d02e957e7b5e7b6ef33e7c100ecc0ea92e7b9e8ace980000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26ae",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "而是想否定那个被强加于我的真名、{00}和真正的使命",
   "zh_hex": "15e89ce7b6e7e6e9bbe867e7b7e828e7f1e8ade854e8798be7b4e820e8ac0200e7d3e820ef3be7b4e83fe853000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26cc",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所以、我……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fbe7f302efcc0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26f1",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……瑟拉？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8aae7c2050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2742",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我从您身上感觉到了力量……{00}您也是新人类吧？",
   "zh_hex": "158be88ae835e88db2e87de8aee7d7e7badae851090900e835e7c0e7b6ef8ab4e841e7d005000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x277b",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你就是拉拉·辛啊……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7c5e7b6e7c2e7c2ef4bea58e7c309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2788",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在弗拉纳冈听过你的传闻、{00}但这样见面还是头一次",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29e9b5e7c2e882eb7ee8d1ef36e7b8e7b4ea38ebac0200e7dbe7b9e7dae85ce862e7f7e7b6e92e87e86400000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27a7",
   "jp_len": 41,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "听说是赤色彗星的得意门生、{00}我还以为会是更厉害的人物呢",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d1e7ede7b6e9e9e89fe9b6b5e7b4e80aef3ce90cb602008be7f7e7f3e7c1e7e2e7b6e952ecbbe988e7b4b4e99ee907000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27d0",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "结果、既不是红色的、{00}动起来也没有3倍速嘛",
   "zh_hex": "15e868e87102e8c4e7b5e7b6e9e3e89fe7b40200ef30e847d9e7c0e7d8e7cb10ed20e9dae936000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27ef",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这下、我稍微松了口气",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9ef4d02efccead5eb58e9e0e7baeabde8ed000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x281c",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那、那是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b702e7b7e7b60909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2854",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……拉拉、从今往后、{00}我便听从你的命令行动",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c2e7c202e88aa2e911e7fe02008be8fae8d1e88ae7b8e7b4e853e94e9fef30000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2885",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……诶？",
   "zh_hex": "150909eaf3050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28a7",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这不是理所当然的吗？毕竟拉拉你更优秀",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7b5e7b6e872e7fbef53e7efe7b4e80205ea2cef2ce7c2e7c2e7b8e952e9afeb0f00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28dd",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "大佐……",
   "zh_hex": "15efa5efba090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28ff",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你做得比我教你的还要出色{00}……要对自己有信心",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e81ce80ae8258beaace7b8e7b4e7f7ef2aafe89f000909ef2ae7beabe8c9e7cbe90fe82d0000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x293f",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好的……大佐",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c7e7b40909efa5efba0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x296d",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "牙买加少佐！再这样下去、就真的……",
   "zh_hex": "15ebd7efa3e854efacefbaef97e80be7b9e7daef4de7eb02e7c5e820e7b40909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29ac",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔呜呜……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81de8d9e8d90909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29c2",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶、撤退！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7de02e90ae880ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a06",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "（瑟拉她……）",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8ee8aae7c2e88e0909ef8f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a10",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "（守护瑟拉的、{00}有我一个人就足够了……！）",
   "zh_hex": "150ae8a8e8e0e8aae7c2e7b40200e7cb8b87e828b4e7c5ea1ee920e7ba0909060b0000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a52",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哎呀呀……总算是解决了",
   "zh_hex": "15e9dce9c6e9c60909e881e889e7b6e89de8abe7ba00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a7f",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……夏亚大佐！",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef37e7d6efa5efbaef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2aa4",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊。立刻开始搜寻爱娜·萨哈林小姐……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c303e86be91fe7fae908ed6defe2e8d5e7eaef4be83be7e8e9b7e83ee9210909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2aff",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是啊、最好能立刻去办",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e7c302e8c5e7c7e7c6e86be91fe7ebe8ea000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b3b",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贵官……",
   "zh_hex": "15e9308f09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b5e",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "基尼亚斯·萨哈林技术少将、负责阿普萨{00}拉斯的开发",
   "zh_hex": "15e829e896e7d6e7c8ef4be83be7e8e9b7ea64ebceeface84a02e92ceba6e7d2e838e83b00e7c2e7c8e7b4e7fae870000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b92",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阿普萨拉斯……那么、是刚才那架机动装{00}甲的？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d2e838e83be7c2e7c80909e7b7e7bd02e7b6e8bce836e7b7e99de7e4ef30e98f00ebdbe7b40500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2bc2",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那架阿普萨拉斯、是足以扭转我军劣势的{00}重要兵器",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e99de7d2e838e83be7c2e7c802e7b6ea1ee7f3ee2be9c2efcce7e0ec0de8fde7b400e8a1ef2aef93e8c3000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2bdd",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可不能在这种偏远的小冲突中、白白失去{00}它",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b5e7c6ef29e7b9e7d1eb4de94ce7b4e83ee95ee8b6ef4e02e809e809e8a5e7eb00e9780000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c15",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "当然、我们也会拼尽全力去搜寻",
   "zh_hex": "15ef53e7ef02efcce7bbe7c0e7e2ea66e8f2efb4efb0e7ebed6defe200000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c48",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请务必如此",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae94fe860e7f0e7ca0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c58",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "总帅直属的我们、可是冒着失去阿普萨拉{00}斯的危险救了诸位",
   "zh_hex": "15e881e9a6e875ea24e7b4efcce7bb02e7c4e7b6eb7fe86de8a5e7ebe7d2e838e83be7c200e7c8e7b4e935e932e8cae7baea56e834000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ca1",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "少将搭救我部下之事、我会转告基西莉亚{00}少将的",
   "zh_hex": "15eface84aeb09e8caefccef70ef4de7cdefb802efcce7e2e9c2e8e5e829e7f8e81ee7d600eface84ae7b4000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ce0",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊、你能这么做就帮大忙了、呵呵呵……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c302e7b8e7c6e7b9e7bde81ce7c5e910efa5ea06e7ba02ef3def3def3d090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d1b",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "基尼亚斯·萨哈林……吗",
   "zh_hex": "15e829e896e7d6e7c8ef4be83be7e8e9b70909e8020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d53",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……你",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b80000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d70",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d91",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你醒过来了啊！太好了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8eb20ef36efcfe7bae7c3ef97e86ae7c7e7ba090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2dc6",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！你、你是！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def97e7b802e7b8e7b6ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2df8",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "走、走开！我才不会向联邦军投降……",
   "zh_hex": "15e89002e890e7faef97efcce836e7b5e7e2efc1ef2eefaae7e0e948e94309090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e2b",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……别管那些、听我说！现在可顾不上分{00}什么敌我！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7e5e93be7b7e8a402e8d1efcce7edef97e82fef29e7c4ea1fe7b5ef4cefae00e7dde7bde7e3efccef9700000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e65",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……诶？",
   "zh_hex": "150909eaf3050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e87",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "离本队漂得太远了",
   "zh_hex": "15e901efa6e7c9ead0e80ae86ae94ce7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e9a",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "剩下的氧气还能撑多久也不知道、想活命{00}就得齐心协力",
   "zh_hex": "15ea3a89e7b4ee49e8ede7f7e7c6ea29e7e9e9dbe7c0e7b5e85ae82a02e7e6e8d4e85300e7c5e80ae924e82de8f6da00000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2efb",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "找到了吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e9d2e7d7e7bae80205000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f23",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "目前为止还没有……",
   "zh_hex": "15efd4ef51e7c1e869e7f7e7d8e7cb090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f79",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊！韦德纳队发来报告！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c3ef97ebaee82ce882e7c9e870efcfe913e8e5ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f88",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他们似乎发现了漂流中的阿普萨拉斯！",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ce7bbe944e933e870e82fe7baead0ea2ec0e7b4e7d2e838e83be7c2e7c806000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2fb3",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "找到了！是阿普萨拉斯！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9d2e7d7e7baef97e7b6e7d2e838e83be7c2e7c8ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2fdb",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "爱娜小姐！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d5e7eae83ee921ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3000",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是……诺里斯！救援终于赶来了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b60909e972ef31e7c8ef97e8cae863e8e2e879ea04efcfe7baef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3035",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是吗……那真是太好了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e8020909e7b7e820e7b6e86ae7c7e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x305e",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "诶……？",
   "zh_hex": "15eaf30909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3080",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我就在这儿等救援、毕竟我可不想当俘虏",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7c5ef29e7b9eb7ce826e8cae86302ea2cef2cefcce7c4e7b5e7e6ef53eadbebee000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x30b7",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可是、就算留在这里……我也不能见死不{00}救！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b602e7c5e889e98cef29e7b9ef310909efcce7c0e7b5e7c6e85cef6ae7b500e8caef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x30ec",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "没事的、我这边的救援也会来的",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d8efb8e7b402efcce7b9e899e7b4e8cae863e7c0e7e2efcfe7b400000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x312c",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3133",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "和我想象中的联邦军、{00}实在是大不相同……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d38be7e6ebf2c0e7b4ef2ed1e7e00200e87fef29e7b6bee7b5e8b1e85d090900000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x314c",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我、叫爱娜·萨哈林",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcc02e8c1e8d5e7eaef4be83be7e8e9b7000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3173",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我、叫天田士郎",
   "zh_hex": "158b02e8c1e844efa0a5eb1f000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3199",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "士郎……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef64eb1f09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x31a0",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……呵呵、真是不可思议呢",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef3def3d02e820e7b6e7b5e7c4efcae8e3e907000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x31ad",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "明明直到刚才、我们还在彼此交战……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef39ef39e875e7d7e8bce83602efcce7bbe7f7ef29efc9e7cae861ef28090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x31c2",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "吉翁和联邦、竟也能互相帮助……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d9ee88e7d3ef2ed102ef2ce7c0e7c6e9f9e8b1e910ea23090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x31d2",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "和你在一起、感觉真不可思议、天田士郎",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d3e7b8ef2987e84702e87de8aee820e7b5e7c4a6e8e302e844efa0a5eb1f00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3201",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我也一样",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcce7c0efb6e7da000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3209",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我恨透了吉翁……",
   "zh_hex": "158be9beed10e7bae7d9ee88090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3216",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可是、自从见到你之后、我却……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b602efb5e88ae85ce7d7e7b8e7cde7fe02efcceadf09090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3252",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "再见了、士郎……",
   "zh_hex": "15e80be85ce7ba02ef64eb1f09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3277",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……啊",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3295",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽然和当初的预定有所出入、但能平安会{00}合、比什么都好",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8e7efe7d3c4eb4fe7b4ea5ae867e7cbe7fbafe89102e7dbe7c6e887e7fce7e200a002e825e7dde7bde840e7c7000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x32d1",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "感谢你们迅速的应对",
   "zh_hex": "15e87de8b2e7b8e7bbed0ee9dae7b4e873e7be000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x32fc",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不必客气……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e860eccbe8ed0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x330a",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "毕竟今后、你们和我就要并肩作战了",
   "zh_hex": "15ea2cef2cefb9e7fe02e7b8e7bbe7d3efcce7c5ef2ae957eb16ef2fef28e7ba00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3343",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么……我来重新介绍一下吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd0909efccefcfe8a1ef8aea84ec87efb6ef4de7d0000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3359",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他就是担任MS队队长的、西……",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ce7c5e7b6e9fde89aefa7ef9ee7c9e7c9ef34e7b402e7f80909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3388",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我是西格·韦德纳中尉",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcce7b6e7f8e824ef4bebaee82ce882ef4eefc60000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x33b0",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "至于我、是瑟蕾因少尉、叫我瑟拉我会很{00}高兴",
   "zh_hex": "15e897e879efcc02e7b6e8aae84cef33efacefc602e8c1efcce8aae7c2efcce7e2e98100e812eaba0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x33ca",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "目前正和西格交往中、副业是当驾驶员",
   "zh_hex": "15d5baef3be7d3e7f8e824e861e911c002ecb6eadae7b6c4e953e975e8490000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3402",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……喂！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8bdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3427",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嗯？……不对吗？我可还不记得自己成了{00}你妻子……",
   "zh_hex": "15e865050909e7b5e7bee80205efcce7c4e7f7e7b5e996e80aefb5e8c9e837e7ba00e7b8ee06e8860909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x346c",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊——……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c3ebafebaf09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3473",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "她性格上虽然多少有些毛病、但是位优秀{00}的新人类……",
   "zh_hex": "15e88ee951e824ef4ce8b8e7efe7e9eface7cbe8a4eb60ed8b02e7dbe7b6e834e9afeb0f00e7b4ef8aefb2e841090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x34af",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "瑟蕾因·伊克斯贝利这名字、弗拉纳冈博{00}士也对我提起过",
   "zh_hex": "15e8aae84cef3304e969e7d5e7c8e857e82ee7b9e8ace98002e9b5e7c2e882eb7eec4d00a5e7c0e7be8be821e847ef3600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x34cb",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "说她是一位具备相当优秀新人类适性的{00}女性",
   "zh_hex": "15e7ede88ee7b687e834ea14e877e8b1c4e9afeb0fef8ab4e841ef41e951e7b400b0e951000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3501",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……非常感谢您",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8f0efc7e87de8b2e835000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x350d",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "至于艾因·雷维曹长、您已经认识了吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e897e879e8d6ef3304e8afea54ed74ef3402e835ef3ae8b7e8a0e92fe7bae7d000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3541",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "刚才那一战、我也看在眼里了",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bce836e7b7efb6ef2802efcce7c0e7f6ef29e90bef31e7ba00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x356e",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请……多多关照",
   "zh_hex": "15e83a0909e7e9e7e9e8bbea1a0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3595",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "以上、便是我布拉德战队的主要成员了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f3ef4c02e8fae7b6efcce831e7c2e82cef28e7c9e7b4e954ef2ae837e849e7ba00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x35cc",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "两名新人类、再加上统领他们的一位队长{00}吗",
   "zh_hex": "15e97de8acef8aefb2e84102e80be854ef4ce929ea20e80ce7bbe7b4efb6e834e7c9ef3400e802000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x35e7",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我很期待诸位的战力、今后就拜托了",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce981eac9eaa8ea56e834e7b4ef28efb002efb9e7fee7c5e91ae7f4e7ba00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3615",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "进展如何？",
   "zh_hex": "15e892e989e7f0efbc050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x363f",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "各舰的整备都在按计划进行、8小时后即{00}可出击",
   "zh_hex": "15e819e7d4e7b4e9fee877e840ef29ea76ea55ea74e892efd602ec44e83eef2de7fee85500e7c4efbee7cc000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3679",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是吗……辛苦了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e8020909ea58e9e6e7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x36a7",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那个、夏亚大佐……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e82802ef37e7d6efa5efba09090500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x36cf",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……大佐是在意联邦军的进攻态势吧？",
   "zh_hex": "150909efa5efbae7b6ef29ef3cef2eefaae7e0e7b4e892ef67e994e8fde7d005000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3705",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是布拉德中佐啊……是啊",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e831e7c2e82cef4eefbae7c30909e7b6e7c3000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3713",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "联邦军的进攻比预想中要快",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ed1e7e0e7b4e8929ee825ea5ae7e6c0ef2ae85f0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3741",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "听说、吉翁本土并没有派出援军",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d1e7ed02e7d9ee88d2ec56e957e7d8e7cbe985afe863e7e000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3778",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "基连总帅似乎认为、凭现有的战力就足以{00}守住",
   "zh_hex": "15e829e86ee881e9a6e944e933e8a0e7c102ea49e82fe7cbe7b4ef28efb0e7c5ea1ee7f300e8a8e8590000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3797",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可对手是那位提安姆中将、不会毫无对策{00}就杀过来",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7beef66e7b6e7b7e834e821e7fce823ef4ee84a02e7b5e7e2ea0ae7dce7beebe400e7c5e89bef36efcf0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x37d4",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "万一也并非不可能……{00}大佐是这么想的吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e9f887e7c0e957e8f0e7b5e7c4e7c6090900bea3e7b6e7b9e7bde7e6e7b4e7d00500000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x380b",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "但愿、我们能及时赶到才好……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dbe96102efcce7bbe7c6e9cfef2dea04e7d7e836e7c709090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8992",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "到、到此为止了吗……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d702e7d7e7cae7c1e869e7bae8020909ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x89d2",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不好！旗舰要是被击毁的话……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e7c7ef97eb0be7d4ef2ae7b6e7f1e7cce97ce7b4e81f090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8a1a",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶、这帮难缠的家伙！亚赞他们到底在{00}干什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7de02e7b9e910e866ec34e7b4e7dfe7fdef97e7d6ec3ee80ce7bbe7d7e9b4ef2900e8d3e7dde7bdef97050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8a69",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "牙买加少佐！",
   "zh_hex": "15ebd7efa3e854efacefbaef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8a73",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "附近正在航行的友军部队、提出愿意协力{00}加入战斗……",
   "zh_hex": "15eaf8efd8ef3bef29e9c1efd6e7b4e960e7e0ef70e7c902e821efbee961ef3ce8f6efb000e854e891ef28e7ff0909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8aaa",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你是要我去请求一般部队协助吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b6ef2aefcce7ebe83ae93aefb6ea80ef70e7c9e8f6ea23e802ef9705000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8ac0",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那种事怎么能答应……不、等一下",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7d1a9e7f2e7bde7c6ea96e8730909e7b502e8268789000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8ad4",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "倒也没必要、{00}什么苦都让我一个人来受……",
   "zh_hex": "15e848e7c0e7d8e860ef2a0200e7dde7bde9e6e840e7f98b87e828b4d9e8c809090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8aec",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "也好、就传令下去、准许他们加入战斗！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c0e7c702e7c5ea38e94eef4de7eb02e87ae8a7e80ce7bbe854e891ef28e7ffef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8b66",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一路辛苦了",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6e8d2ea58e9e6e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8b73",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "感谢你将这条『宇宙世纪路线』一直玩到{00}了最后",
   "zh_hex": "15e87de8b2e7b8e84ae7b9e9d40ce8bee8bfe83ceb99e8d2e9160defb6e875e970e7d700e7bae8c5e7fe000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8b93",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "另外、隆德·贝尔队的战斗在此暂告一段{00}落……",
   "zh_hex": "15e99be8f702ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e7b4ef28e7ffef29e7cae9ffe8e5efb6ea6b00e92a0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8bb2",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "游戏本身仍可继续、之后也希望你能玩下{00}去",
   "zh_hex": "15ea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02e7cde7fee7c0e87be965e7b8e7c6e970ef4d00e7eb00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8bd7",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "此外、为一路玩到最后的你、还准备了特{00}别关卡",
   "zh_hex": "15e7cae8f702e7c1efb6e8d2e970e7d7e8c5e7fee7b4e7b802e7f7e87ae877e7bae7cf00e7e5e8bbe80100000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8bfe",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是与另一条战线作战的大天使队的特别{00}演习",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e832e99befb6e9d4ef28e916ef2fef28e7b4efa5e844e83fe7c9e7b4e7cfe7e500ea2feab6000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8c1f",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "与他们一战、检验一下你亲手培养的部队{00}也不错",
   "zh_hex": "15e832e80ce7bbefb6ef2802ee40ea99efb6ef4de7b8e894ef66edfeec0be7b4ef70e7c900e7c0e7b5e885000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8c44",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特别演习』、即可与{00}他们交战",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29abe8a6e7beef28c0e966eaaa0ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d02e855e7c4e83200e80ce7bbe861ef280000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8c69",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、『SD高达G世代DS』",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd020cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83ce8e7ef96ef9e0d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8c8d",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后也希望你能尽情地玩到最后",
   "zh_hex": "15efb9e7fee7c0e87be965e7b8e7c6e8f2e88bef63e970e7d7e8c5e7fe0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8d06",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "谢谢你一路陪着我这个不太可靠的舰长",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b2e8b2e7b8efb6e8d2ef42e86defcce7b9e828e7b5e86ae7c4e8c7e7b4e7d4ef340000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8d25",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『平成高达路线』就到此结束了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce887e837e812ef2be8d2e9160de7c5e7d7e7cae868e895e7ba000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8d43",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、虽说我们预防者的战斗已经结束了{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602e8b8e7edefcce7bbea5ae968ef6ee7b4ef28e7ffef3ae8b7e868e895e7ba00090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8d5d",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……游戏本身仍可继续、之后也请继续享{00}受游戏哦",
   "zh_hex": "150909ea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02e7cde7fee7c0e83ae9d6e9adec0600e8c8ea94ea3ee91900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8d83",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为将这条线玩到最后的你、还准备了新的{00}关卡哦",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1e84ae7b9e9d4e916e970e7d7e8c5e7fee7b4e7b802e7f7e87ae877e7baef8ae7b400e8bbe801e91900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8da7",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是与我们分头、和提坦斯及新吉翁作战{00}的……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e8328be7bbcde92e02e7d3e821e843e7c8e9cfef8ae7d9ee88ef2fef2800e7b4090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8dc2",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……与隆德·贝尔队进行的特别演习哦",
   "zh_hex": "150909e832ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e892efd6e7b4e7cfe7e5ea2feab6e9190000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8dd5",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特别演习』、就能与{00}他们交战哦",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efb5e8a6e7beef28ef4ee966eaaa0ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d02e7c5e7c6e83200e80ce7bbe861ef28e91900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8dfb",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请务必来挑战哦",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae94fe860efcfeae7ef28e919000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8e09",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、『SD高达G世代DS』",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd020cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83ce8e7ef96ef9e0d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8e2d",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『自由对战的战火！冲破重围吧、大天使{00}号！』",
   "zh_hex": "150cefb5e8a6e7beef28e7b4ef28e8daef97e95eef6de8a1e9dee7d002efa5e844e83f00e833ef970d0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8eae",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是主天使号舰长、娜塔尔·巴基露露中{00}佐",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6e954e844e83fe833e7d4ef3402e7eae945e7e1ef4be85be829e858e858ef4e00efba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8ebe",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "首先、我要向贵官一路以来出色的指挥致{00}以敬意",
   "zh_hex": "15ef40b8028bef2a9de9308f87e8d2e7f3d9afe89fe7b4e8c0e949ea3200e7f3ee38ef3c00000000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8ee0",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "多亏贵官的协力、我们才得以一路战斗到{00}最后",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e9eab7e930ef92e7b4e8f6efb002efcce7bbe836e80ae7f3efb6e8d2ef28e7ffe7d700e8c5e7fe0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8f02",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『对手路线』就到此结束了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce7beef66e8d2e9160de7c5e7d7e7cae868e895e7ba00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8f18",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、我们主天使队的战斗虽然到此结束{00}了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602efcce7bbe954e844e83fe7c9e7b4ef28e7ffe8b8e7efe7d7e7cae868e89500e7ba0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8f31",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "游戏本身仍可继续、之后也希望你能玩下{00}去",
   "zh_hex": "15ea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02e7cde7fee7c0e87be965e7b8e7c6e970ef4d00e7eb0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8f55",
   "jp_len": 43,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "自由对战之后仍可继续、而且选择『特别{00}演习』、就能……",
   "zh_hex": "15efb5e8a6e7beef28e7cde7feeab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02e89ce999e966eaaa0ce7cfe7e500ea2feab60d02e7c5e7c6090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8f80",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "还能与隆德·贝尔、预防者进行联合演习",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f7e7c6e832ed16e82cef4be857e7e102ea5ae968ef6ee892efd6ef2eefc0ea2feab60000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8f9e",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我相信、以贵官的本事、与他们一战也定{00}能取胜",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce8b1e90f02e7f3e930ef92e7b4efa6efb802e832e80ce7bbefb6ef28e7c0e86700e7c6e987e8db000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8fc3",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、『SD高达G世代DS』",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd020cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83ce8e7ef96ef9e0d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8fe7",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "愿贵官今后也能奋战不懈",
   "zh_hex": "15e961e9308fa2e7fee7c0e7c6ef46ef28e7b5ec6f0000000000"
  }
 ]
}
